OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,FA doctors' trade union has warned that
OL,7,Fwithout "transformative" and urgent
OL,8,Freforms, the NHS will struggle to see
OL,9,Fout another New Year.
OL,11,FDr Iain Kennedy, chairman of the
OL,12,FBritish Medical Association (BMA)
OL,13,FScotland, said in his annual New Year
OL,14,Fmessage on Tuesday that current
OL,15,Fevidence suggests there will be a
OL,16,Flarge increase in people who don't
OL,17,Fbelieve the NHS can provide them with
OL,18,Fadequate care, forcing them to go
OL,19,Fprivate.
