OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,FBMA Scotland published results from
OL,7,Fits annual winter pressures survey, in
OL,8,Fwhich some 980 doctors took part.
OL,10,FSome 99% of respondents said they are
OL,11,Feither extremely concerned (76%) or
OL,12,Fconcerned (23%) about the impact of
OL,13,Fincreased pressures on the NHS
OL,14,Fthroughout winter.
OL,16,F70% said the NHS is in "crisis mode"
OL,17,Fall year round, and 29% said they
OL,18,Fbelieve it is in crisis mode often,
OL,19,Fbut not always.
