OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,F84% do not believe the NHS has enough
OL,7,Fstaff to cope with the increase in
OL,8,Fdemand this winter, and 12% said they
OL,9,Fare unsure.
OL,11,F86% said they had no confidence that
OL,12,Fthe Scottish Government would give the
OL,13,FNHS sustainable funding, and 13% said
OL,14,Fthey were unsure.
OL,16,FOf those who responded to the survey,
OL,17,F98% had no (86%), or were not sure if
OL,18,Fthey had (13%), confidence in the
OL,19,FScottish Government to put the NHS on
OL,20,Fa sustainable footing
