OL,6,FAnother says: "We feel like we are
OL,7,Fsinking. We are working hard to get
OL,8,Fpatients fit for theatre, but the lack
OL,9,Fof elective beds means we continue to
OL,10,Fcancel patients. We can never get on
OL,11,Ftop of elective surgery demand with
OL,12,Fthe model we currently have."
OL,14,FOne GP wrote: "Been crisis mode here
OL,15,Ffor months. Critical incident in
OL,16,FNovember.
OL,18,F"Feels like nobody in management `
OL,19,Facute sector or community is listening
OL,20,For actually admitting the seriousness
OL,21,Fof the situation at all levels.
