OL,6,F"This has and continues to have an
OL,7,Fimpact on lives let alone safety and
OL,8,Fstaff morale."
OL,10,FOther testimonials cited similar
OL,11,Fissues of lack of staffing, bed
OL,12,Fshortages and employees being
OL,13,Fstretched thin.
OL,15,FDr Kennedy warned the "time for words
OL,16,Fhas passed" and that in 2025, there
OL,17,Fmust be "action in the form of reform".
