OL,6,FHe added: "Doctors are finding
OL,7,Fthemselves working in a system that is
OL,8,Fneither prepared nor staffed
OL,9,Fadequately.
OL,11,F"They are struggling to cope in an NHS
OL,12,Fthat is in constant crisis, which is
OL,13,Fboth mentally and physically
OL,14,Fexhausting."
