OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,FHe added: "We know the NHS is valued
OL,7,Fand that, politically, all agree with
OL,8,Fthe founding principle of 'free at the
OL,9,Fpoint of need'. What needs to be put
OL,10,Fin place are measures that protect our
OL,11,Fhealth service for the long term,
OL,12,Fgiving the system stability and
OL,13,Fpatients peace of mind.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
