OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,F"The measures need to be
OL,7,Ftransformative; the NHS needs to be
OL,8,Freformed, we cannot continue to simply
OL,9,Fplug gaps with short-term funding,
OL,10,Fthere needs to be a whole system
OL,11,Fapproach, looking at primary,
OL,12,Fsecondary and social care, how they
OL,13,Fare appropriately funded and how they
OL,14,Finteract."
OL,16,F"We know that the pressures we are
OL,17,Fseeing on the acute services are
OL,18,Flinked to lack of resources in general
OL,19,Fpractice and social care, so to help
OL,20,Fguide the overall reform we need an
OL,21,Furgent, comprehensive workforce plan."
