OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,FCiting the doctors' doubts on Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment funding, he said: "Doctors
OL,8,Fhave heard a lot of warm words
OL,9,Frecently from the First Minister and
OL,10,Fhis team about the NHS being at the
OL,11,Fheart of their recent budget, but
OL,12,Fwords must be matched with a clear
OL,13,Fvision, a timetable for reform and
OL,14,Faction.
OL,26,@oD@^OU
