OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,F"The NHS as we know it will struggle
OL,7,Fto see out another year, as its
OL,8,Ffounding principles, which we all
OL,9,Fvalue so highly will be at risk with
OL,10,Fmore and more people forced to go
OL,11,Fprivate or simply left to suffer as
OL,12,Fthey cannot access the care they need,
OL,13,Fwhen they need it."
OL,15,FHealth Secretary Neil Gray agreed with
OL,16,Fthe BMA's stance on reform and said
OL,17,Fthe Scottish Government is listening
OL,18,Fto patient and clinical opinions to
OL,19,Fsteer how it delivers services.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]
