OL,3,CDoctors' union warns NHS will struggle
OL,4,Cto last another year without reform
OL,6,FHe added: "The measures we set out in
OL,7,Fthe draft Budget, including record #21
OL,8,Fbillion investment for health and
OL,9,Fsocial care, would mean quicker
OL,10,Ftreatments, more GP appointments, and
OL,11,Fworld-class facilities for people
OL,12,Facross Scotland.
OL,14,F"But we will only be able to deliver
OL,15,Fthese transformational investments and
OL,16,Fdrive further improvements for
OL,17,Fpatients if our Budget is agreed. I
OL,18,Furge Parliament to unite behind it."
